          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h1><strong>Ambassador </strong>Affiliate<strong> Programme</strong></h1><h3><em>Turn your network into long-term value</em></h3><h2><strong>Your Role</strong></h2><p>As a <strong>RŌ Ambassador</strong>, you represent the brand on the ground:</p><ul><li>Introducing RŌ to retailers, outfitters, and partners</li><li>Opening doors in your local market</li><li>Supporting the growth of a responsible outdoor brand</li></ul><h2><strong>Earnings Structure</strong></h2><h3><strong>Retail Introduction Commission</strong></h3><p>Earn <strong>up to 2.5% on all net sales</strong> generated from retail partners you introduce.</p><h3><strong>Tiered Model</strong></h3><h3>Tier Criteria Commission </h3><ul><li>Explorer First successful partner <strong>1.5%</strong></li><li>Pathfinder2–4 active partners <strong>2.0%</strong></li><li>Trailblazer 5+ partners or £50k+ annual sales <strong>2.5%</strong></li></ul><h2><strong>What Qualifies as an Introduction</strong></h2><p>An introduction is considered successful when:</p><ul><li>You connect RŌ directly with a retail partner</li><li>The partner opens an account</li><li>The partner places their first order within 90 days</li></ul><h2><strong>Commission Terms</strong></h2><ul><li>Paid on <strong>net invoiced sales</strong> (excluding VAT and returns)</li><li>Paid <strong>quarterly</strong></li><li>Valid for <strong>up to 36 months</strong> from first order</li></ul><h2><strong>Performance Incentives</strong></h2><ul><li>First partner onboarded → <strong>£100 bonus</strong></li><li>Three partners onboarded → <strong>£250 bonus</strong></li><li>Five or more partners → <strong>£500 bonus</strong></li></ul><h2><strong>Beyond Commission</strong></h2><p>Being a <strong>RŌ Ambassador</strong> is about more than earning:</p><ul><li>Free Product</li><li>Early access to new releases</li><li>Exclusive ambassador-only product</li><li>Features across RŌ channels</li><li>Opportunities to support or lead brand adventures</li><li>Direct involvement in shaping the brand’s future</li></ul><h1><strong>Affiliate Programme</strong></h1><h3><em>For digital reach and content creators</em></h3><ul><li>Personal referral link + code</li><li><strong>5-10% commission</strong> on direct online sales</li><li>30-day tracking window</li></ul><h1><strong>Principles</strong></h1><p>To protect the brand and community:</p><ul><li><strong>First introduction wins</strong> (relationship ownership)</li><li>Retail partners must align with RŌ values</li><li>Consistent pricing must be respected across all channels</li></ul><h1><strong>Positioning</strong></h1><p>This isn’t a typical ambassador scheme.</p><p><strong>It’s a way to build something with RŌ—and share in its growth.</strong></p><h1><strong>Example</strong></h1><p>Introduce 3 retail partners:</p><ul><li>Each order £40,000 annually</li><li>Total = £120,000</li><li>At 2.5% → <strong>£3,000 per year</strong> (for up to 36 months)</li></ul><h1><strong>Getting Started</strong></h1><ol><li>Apply</li><li>Get approved</li><li>Receive your RŌ Ambassador Toolkit and sample product</li><li>Start making introductions</li></ol><h2><strong>RŌ Adventure</strong></h2><p><em>Gear for your next adventure. Built from yesterday’s waste.</em></p>"
          }
        }
